author: dkhaywood
msg: In JavaIntrospector#findAndCreateFieldPeers, no longer go looking for properties for "value" types (as per ValueTypeRegistry); instead just find the collections and then find the properties.
This is significant because this was the only place where ValueTypeRegistry is basically used; so can now get rid of.
